data.description: Welcome to this lovely pond home in the highly desirable Northwest Bradenton area. This home is located in an area with no HOA, no CDD, and no deed restrictions. It features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a 2-car garage, a remodeled kitchen with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances, newer flooring, and interior paint. The home had hurricane windows and doors installed in 2019, AC was installed in 2018, and the water heater in 2023. The master bedroom is large with it's own en-suite bathroom. The large yard is fully fenced with plenty of room for a pool, and with the pond-fed sprinkler system it makes it easy and inexpensive to maintain. Watch all the birds, turtles, and otters in the pond located directly behind the house. This home is located just minutes from Anna Maria Island, Warner's Bayou boat ramp, Robinson Preserve, Palma Sola Botanical Park, and DeSoto National Park. Most of the furniture is included (optional). Hurry, as this house will not last!
